 2789  1246  CA 52 12     	JZ NINPUT                       ;Code for + sign. Jump ahead if code for + sign.
 2790  1249  FE AD        	CPI 0ADH                        ;See if code for minus (-) sign.
 2791  124B  C2 55 12     	JNZ NOTPLM                      ;Jump ahead if not code for minus sign. If code for
