 2803  1268  FE B0        	CPI 0B0H                        ;If not end of string, check to see
 2804  126A  FA C5 09     	JM NUMERR                       ;If character represents
 2805  126D  FE BA        	CPI 0BAH                        ;A valid decimal number (0 to 9)
