 2973  13A7  21 1F 00     OUTNEG:	LXI H,FPACC                     ;If number in FPACC is negative must negate in order
 2974  13AA  06 03        	MVI B,003H                      ;To display. Set pntr to LSW of FPACC & set prec. cntr.
 2975  13AC  CD 75 11     	CALL COMPLM                     ;Negate the number in the FPACC to make it positive
